cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.IT. 

The paper discusses the power of depth for feedforward neural networks, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves the analysis of the approximation capability of neural networks, which falls under the scope of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper uses mathematical techniques to prove the main result, which is related to information theory, so cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a possible sub-category.
